{"tid":191622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[陰鳩公] 自由黨提名廿蚊張做教育局長","createTime":"2017-04-08T04:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T05:32:58.000Z","uid":41205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43d561ab8a323eca1480cb4b8975968bdde2a286","tid":191622,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:59:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/211666/%e3%80%90%e5%80%99%e4%bb%bb%e7%89%b9%e9%a6%96%e3%80%91%e5%bc%b5%e5%ae%87%e4%ba%ba%e7%8d%b2%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e9%bb%a8%e6%8e%a8%e8%96%a6%e7%95%b6%e6%95%99%e8%82%b2%e5%b1%80%e9%95%b7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F211666%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%2580%2599%25e4%25bb%25bb%25e7%2589%25b9%25e9%25a6%2596%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%25bc%25b5%25e5%25ae%2587%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%258d%25b2%25e8%2587%25aa%25e7%2594%25b1%25e9%25bb%25a8%25e6%258e%25a8%25e8%2596%25a6%25e7%2595%25b6%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2582%25b2%25e5%25b1%2580%25e9%2595%25b7%2F&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=46a5dc5c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/211666/%e3%80%90%e5%80%99%e4%bb%bb%e7%89%b9%e9%a6%96%e3%80%91%e5%bc%b5%e5%ae%87%e4%ba%ba%e7%8d%b2%e8%87%aa%e7%94%b1%e9%bb%a8%e6%8e%a8%e8%96%a6%e7%95%b6%e6%95%99%e8%82%b2%e5%b1%80%e9%95%b7/</a><br />\n<br />\n候任特首林鄭月娥明日便要上京接受任命，但籌組班子進程似乎並不順利之際，自由黨黨魁鍾國斌，在今日now新聞台播出的專訪節目《大鳴大放》片段中就指，自由黨會向林鄭月娥推薦黨主席張宇人，除了可以繼續當行政會議成員外，也可當教育局局長。<br />\n<br />\n鍾國斌解釋，張宇人熟悉教育，又能配合林鄭月娥施政。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，張宇人早前曾代表自由黨解釋，為何不參與聯署要求當局取消小三TSA，是因為自由黨只認為，問題在港府如何令學生沒有壓力，不在考試本身。至於自由黨此舉是否是向林鄭月娥「索價」的策略，也令公眾有理由質疑。<br />\n<br />\n另外，民主黨創黨主席李柱銘，昨日在接受傳媒專訪時，向林鄭月娥開出兩大條件，即要在任內重啟政改，及要在籌組班子時證明沒有「西環治港」，才可接受調整民主黨跟林鄭月娥的合作關係，不再要求黨員加入政府前要退黨。<br />\n<br />\n（原圖為蘋果日報圖片）"},{"pid":"093407910288e4e97ba19a4f353ccad1a145a35d","tid":191622,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:12:33.000Z","msg":"不如做勞工及福利局局長吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29bb02bd1bb26f30de9028a1652016538b0f1926","tid":191622,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:12:58.000Z","msg":"教師時薪$20"},{"pid":"4492b56ac0b918bac728d3f1ebc2c7a25cb6edde","tid":191622,"uid":13450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:21:01.000Z","msg":"佢個仔做教師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e3cc17caa58b5ae36c0bd4f42ceb198c78103e","tid":191622,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:23:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70bd116c03c8c53c6b628bda2889804e5c2a3c51","tid":191622,"uid":68568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:25:34.000Z","msg":"每間學校20蚊做生涯規劃"},{"pid":"c0d6c4b477c5961bd5a591cf37482a612f1e1194","tid":191622,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:29:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每間學校20蚊做生涯規劃</blockquote><br />\n全部撥款都係廿蚊./."},{"pid":"6a9271f0e657dab872590350ef32b1be27d35fed","tid":191622,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如做勞工及福利局局長吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗起都爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港畜打工仔有福了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}